@startuml
[*] --> Order
Order --> Arrival: plane arrives
Arrival --> Preparation: prepare plane
Preparation --> Operations: condition good and schedule allows
Preparation --> Maintenance: condition poor or no more scheduled flights
Operations --> Maintenance: maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation: serviced and ready for operations
Mainline --> OutOfService: permanently withdrawn from service
OutOfService --> [*]
InService --> OutOfService: plane taken out of service
InService --> Maintenance: no more scheduled flights
@enduml
